			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~t0qer">t0qer</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~t0qer">( 230538 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64252342">		
		on Monday February 19, 2024 @03:36PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23231722&amp;cid=64252342">#64252342</a>)
		<small><a href="http://www.kaillera.com/forums/viewtopic.php?topic=1743&forum=5&0" title="http://www.kaillera.com/forums/viewtopic.php?topic=1743&forum=5&0" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a>
